ant of 1948.137)||Private collection||Germany\n|-\n|107||[[File:Frans Hals 101 WGA version.jpg|150px]]||Portrait of an unknown man, possibly [[Albert van Nierop]]||c.1640||120 x 95&nbsp;cm||WRM 2529 (pendant of WRM 2530)||Wallraf-Richartz-Museum||Cologne\n|-\n|108||[[File:Frans Hals 102 WGA version.jpg|150px]]||Portrait of an unknown woman, possibly Cornelia van der Meer||c.1640||120 x 94.5&nbsp;cm||WRM 2530 (pendant of WRM 2529)||[[Wallraf-Richartz-Museum]]||Cologne\n|-\n|109||[[File:Frans Hals - left pendant of male pendant pair.jpg|150px]]||Portrait of a man facing right||1640\u20131642||29.5 x 23.5&nbsp;cm||||Staatliche Kunstsammlungen||Kassel, DE\n|-\n|110||[[File:Frans Hals - right pendant of male pendant pair.jpg|150px]]||Portrait of a man facing left||1640\u20131642||30.5 x 24.5&nbsp;cm||||Staatliche Kunstsammlungen||Kassel, DE\n|-\n|111||[[File:Frans Hals - Malle Babbe - WGA11105.jpg|150px]]||Drinking woman ([[Malle Babbe]]) with an owl on her shoulder||1630\u20131635||75 x 64&nbsp;cm||801C ||Gem\u00e4ldegalerie||Berlin\n|-\n|112||[[File:Frans Hals - Regents of the St Elizabeth Hospital of Haarlem - WGA11139.jpg|150px]]||Regenten of the [[Grote of St. Elisabeth Gasthuis, Haarlem]] 1641||1641||153 x 252&nbsp;cm||OSI-114 ||Frans Hals Museum||Haarlem\n|-\n|113||[[File:Frans Hals 078.jpg|150px]]||Portrait of Mr. Bodolphe||1643||122.4 \u00d7 97.5&nbsp;cm||1961.18.23 (pendant to 1961.18.24)||Yale University Art Gallery||New Haven, CT\n|-\n|114||[[File:Frans Hals 048.jpg|150px]]||[[Portrait of Mrs. Bodolphe]]||1643||122.4 \u00d7 97.5&nbsp;cm||1961.18.24 (pendant to 1961.18.23)||[[Yale University Art Gallery]]||New Haven, CT\n|-\n|115||[[File:Frans Hals - portrait of an elderly man facing right with hat and ruff collar.jpg|150px]]||Portrait of an elderly man facing right with hat and ruff collar||1643||92.7 x 75&nbsp;cm||||private collection||unknown\n|-\n|116||[[File:Frans Hals - Portrait of a man with a hand on his heart.jpg|150px]]||Portrait of a man||1640\u2013