994)\n!Peak<br>position\n|-\n{{singlechart|Australia|44|artist=Haddaway|song=I Miss You}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Austria|11|artist=Haddaway|song=I Miss You}}\n|- \n{{singlechart|Flanders|26|artist=Haddaway|song=I Miss You}}\n|-\n|Denmark ([[IFPI Denmark|IFPI]])\n|align=\"center\"|18\n|-\n|Europe ([[Eurochart Hot 100]])<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://americanradiohistory.com/Archive-Music-and-Media/90s/1994/MM-1994-02-19.pdf|title=Eurochart Hot 100 Singles|work=[[Music & Media]]|date=February 19, 1994|accessdate=March 28, 2018|format=PDF}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|10\n|-\n|Finland ([[Suomen virallinen lista]])<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=FwgEAAAAMBAJ&q=hits+of+the+world#v=onepage&q&f=false Billboard: January 15, 1994]</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|4\n|-\n{{singlechart|France|16|artist=Haddaway|song=I Miss You}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Germany|18|artist=Haddaway|song=I Miss You}}\n|-\n|Iceland ([[\u00cdslenski listinn|\u00cdslenski Listinn Topp 40]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timarit.is/files/12110136.pdf#navpanes=1&view=FitH|title=\u00cdslenski Listinn Topp 40 (27.01.1994 - 02.02.1993)|publisher=Dagbla\u00f0i\u00f0 V\u00edsir - T\u00f3nlist|accessdate=March 28, 2018|language= is}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|25\n|-\n|Ireland ([[Irish Recorded Music Association|IRMA]])<ref>Irish Singles Chart [http://www.irishcharts.ie/search/placement Irishcharts.ie]  {{webarchive|url=https://www.webcitation.org/5hFf8iFDu?url=http://www.irishcharts.ie/search/placement |date=2009-06-03 }} (Retrieved February 10, 2008)</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|13\n|-\n{{singlechart|Dutch40|21|artist=Haddaway|song=I Miss You}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Dutch100|17|artist=Haddaway|song=I Miss You}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Sweden|36|artist=Haddaway|song=I Miss You}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Swiss|17|artist=Haddaway|song=I Miss You}}\n|-\n|[[UK Singles Chart|UK Singles]] ([[Official Charts Company]])<ref>\"I Miss You\", UK Singles Chart [https://www.officialcharts.com/search/singles/Warfair Official Charts Company] (Retrieved Aug